Description: Professional VPS Provisioning Tool with 13 Containerized Stacks
 VPS Installer is an enterprise-grade tool for automated provisioning and 
 management of containerized services on Linux VPS servers.
 .
 Supported stacks:
  - Traefik (Reverse Proxy + SSL/TLS)
  - Portainer (Docker Management UI)
  - Chatwoot (Customer Support Platform)
  - n8n (Workflow Automation)
  - Evolution (Email Server)
  - Evo-AI (AI Integration)
  - Prometheus + Grafana (Monitoring)
  - PostgreSQL + Redis (Data Layer)
  - Backup Scheduler (Automated Backups)
  - SSH Configuration (Security Hardening)
  - Restore Backups (Interactive Recovery)
  - Odoo 17.0 (ERP System)
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive and non-interactive installation modes
  - Automatic backup with flexible scheduling
  - Security hardening with SSH ed25519 keys
  - Health checks on all services
  - CI/CD ready with environment-based configuration
  - Professional documentation and troubleshooting guides
